{"work":"KJV + Strong's","code":"Hab","book":"Habakkuk","chapterCount":3,"chapters":[{"number":1,"verses":[{"id":"Hab|1|1","reference":"Habakkuk 1:1","number":1,"text":"The burden which Habakkuk the prophet did see.","strongs":[{"label":"The burden","strongsId":"H4853"},{"label":"which Habakkuk","strongsId":"H2265"},{"label":"the prophet","strongsId":"H5030"}]},{"id":"Hab|1|2","reference":"Habakkuk 1:2","number":2,"text":"O LORD, how long shall I cry, and thou wilt not hear! <em>even</em> cry out unto thee <em>of</em> violence, and thou wilt not save!","strongs":[{"label":"O LORD","strongsId":"H3068"},{"label":"how long shall I cry","strongsId":"H7768"},{"label":"and thou wilt not hear","strongsId":"H8085"},{"label":"em>even</em> cry out","strongsId":"H2199"},{"label":"unto thee <em>of</em> violence","strongsId":"H2555"}]},{"id":"Hab|1|3","reference":"Habakkuk 1:3","number":3,"text":"Why dost thou shew me iniquity, and cause <em>me</em> to behold grievance? for spoiling and violence <em>are</em> before me: and there are <em>that</em> raise up strife and contention.","strongs":[{"label":"Why dost thou shew","strongsId":"H7200"},{"label":"me iniquity","strongsId":"H205"},{"label":"and cause <em>me</em> to behold","strongsId":"H5027"},{"label":"grievance","strongsId":"H5999"},{"label":"for spoiling","strongsId":"H7701"},{"label":"and violence","strongsId":"H2555"},{"label":"em>are</em> before me: and there are <em>that</em> raise up","strongsId":"H5375"},{"label":"strife","strongsId":"H7379"}]},{"id":"Hab|1|4","reference":"Habakkuk 1:4","number":4,"text":"Therefore the law is slacked, and judgment doth never go forth: for the wicked doth compass about the righteous; therefore wrong judgment proceedeth.","strongs":[{"label":"Therefore the law","strongsId":"H8451"},{"label":"is slacked","strongsId":"H6313"},{"label":"and judgment","strongsId":"H4941"},{"label":"doth never","strongsId":"H5331"},{"label":"go forth","strongsId":"H3318"},{"label":"for the wicked","strongsId":"H7563"},{"label":"doth compass","strongsId":"H3803"},{"label":"about the righteous","strongsId":"H6662"},{"label":"therefore wrong","strongsId":"H6127"},{"label":"judgment","strongsId":"H4941"}]},{"id":"Hab|1|5","reference":"Habakkuk 1:5","number":5,"text":"Behold ye among the heathen, and regard, and wonder marvellously: for <em>I</em> will work a work in your days, <em>which</em> ye will not believe, though it be told","strongs":[{"label":"Behold","strongsId":"H7200"},{"label":"ye among the heathen","strongsId":"H1471"},{"label":"and regard","strongsId":"H5027"},{"label":"and wonder","strongsId":"H8539"},{"label":"marvellously","strongsId":"H8539"},{"label":"for <em>I</em> will work","strongsId":"H6466"},{"label":"a work","strongsId":"H6467"},{"label":"in your days","strongsId":"H3117"},{"label":"em>which</em> ye will not believe","strongsId":"H539"}]},{"id":"Hab|1|6","reference":"Habakkuk 1:6","number":6,"text":"For, lo, I raise up the Chaldeans, <em>that</em> bitter and hasty nation, which shall march through the breadth of the land, to possess the dwellingplaces","strongs":[{"label":"For, lo, I raise up","strongsId":"H6965"},{"label":"the Chaldeans","strongsId":"H3778"},{"label":"em>that</em> bitter","strongsId":"H4751"},{"label":"and hasty","strongsId":"H4116"},{"label":"nation","strongsId":"H1471"},{"label":"which shall march","strongsId":"H1980"},{"label":"through the breadth","strongsId":"H4800"},{"label":"of the land","strongsId":"H776"},{"label":"to possess","strongsId":"H3423"}]},{"id":"Hab|1|7","reference":"Habakkuk 1:7","number":7,"text":"They <em>are</em> terrible and dreadful: their judgment and their dignity shall proceed","strongs":[{"label":"They <em>are</em> terrible","strongsId":"H366"},{"label":"and dreadful","strongsId":"H3372"},{"label":"their judgment","strongsId":"H4941"},{"label":"and their dignity","strongsId":"H7613"}]},{"id":"Hab|1|8","reference":"Habakkuk 1:8","number":8,"text":"Their horses also are swifter than the leopards, and are more fierce than the evening wolves: and their horsemen shall spread themselves, and their horsemen shall come from far; they shall fly as the eagle <em>that</em> hasteth to eat.","strongs":[{"label":"Their horses","strongsId":"H5483"},{"label":"also are swifter","strongsId":"H7043"},{"label":"than the leopards","strongsId":"H5246"},{"label":"and are more fierce","strongsId":"H2300"},{"label":"than the evening","strongsId":"H6153"},{"label":"wolves","strongsId":"H2061"},{"label":"and their horsemen","strongsId":"H6571"},{"label":"shall spread","strongsId":"H6335"},{"label":"themselves, and their horsemen","strongsId":"H6571"},{"label":"shall come","strongsId":"H935"},{"label":"from far","strongsId":"H7350"},{"label":"they shall fly","strongsId":"H5774"},{"label":"as the eagle","strongsId":"H5404"},{"label":"em>that</em> hasteth","strongsId":"H2363"}]},{"id":"Hab|1|9","reference":"Habakkuk 1:9","number":9,"text":"They shall come all for violence: their faces shall sup up <em>as</em> the east wind, and they shall gather the captivity as the sand.","strongs":[{"label":"They shall come","strongsId":"H935"},{"label":"all for violence","strongsId":"H2555"},{"label":"their faces","strongsId":"H6440"},{"label":"shall sup up","strongsId":"H4041"},{"label":"em>as</em> the east wind","strongsId":"H6921"},{"label":"and they shall gather","strongsId":"H622"},{"label":"the captivity","strongsId":"H7628"}]},{"id":"Hab|1|10","reference":"Habakkuk 1:10","number":10,"text":"And they shall scoff at the kings, and the princes shall be a scorn unto them: they shall deride every strong hold; for they shall heap dust, and take","strongs":[{"label":"And they shall scoff","strongsId":"H7046"},{"label":"at the kings","strongsId":"H4428"},{"label":"and the princes","strongsId":"H7336"},{"label":"shall be a scorn","strongsId":"H4890"},{"label":"unto them: they shall deride","strongsId":"H7832"},{"label":"every strong hold","strongsId":"H4013"},{"label":"for they shall heap","strongsId":"H6651"},{"label":"dust","strongsId":"H6083"}]},{"id":"Hab|1|11","reference":"Habakkuk 1:11","number":11,"text":"Then shall <em>his</em> mind change, and he shall pass over, and offend, <em>imputing</em> this his power unto his god.","strongs":[{"label":"Then shall <em>his</em> mind","strongsId":"H7307"},{"label":"change","strongsId":"H2498"},{"label":"and he shall pass over","strongsId":"H5674"},{"label":"and offend","strongsId":"H816"},{"label":"em>imputing</em> this","strongsId":"H2098"},{"label":"his power","strongsId":"H3581"}]},{"id":"Hab|1|12","reference":"Habakkuk 1:12","number":12,"text":"<em>Art</em> thou not from everlasting, O LORD my God, mine Holy One? we shall not die. O LORD, thou hast ordained them for judgment; and, O mighty God, thou hast established them for correction.","strongs":[{"label":"em>Art</em> thou not from everlasting","strongsId":"H6924"},{"label":"O LORD","strongsId":"H3068"},{"label":"my God","strongsId":"H430"},{"label":"mine Holy One","strongsId":"H6918"},{"label":"we shall not die","strongsId":"H4191"},{"label":"O LORD","strongsId":"H3068"},{"label":"thou hast ordained","strongsId":"H7760"},{"label":"them for judgment","strongsId":"H4941"},{"label":"and, O mighty God","strongsId":"H6697"},{"label":"thou hast established","strongsId":"H3245"}]},{"id":"Hab|1|13","reference":"Habakkuk 1:13","number":13,"text":"<em>Thou art</em> of purer eyes than to behold evil, and canst not look on iniquity: wherefore lookest thou upon them that deal treacherously, <em>and</em> holdest thy tongue when the wicked devoureth <em>the man that is</em> more righteous","strongs":[{"label":"em>Thou art</em> of purer","strongsId":"H2889"},{"label":"eyes","strongsId":"H5869"},{"label":"than to behold","strongsId":"H7200"},{"label":"evil","strongsId":"H7451"},{"label":"and canst","strongsId":"H3201"},{"label":"not look","strongsId":"H5027"},{"label":"on iniquity","strongsId":"H5999"},{"label":"wherefore lookest","strongsId":"H5027"},{"label":"thou upon them that deal treacherously","strongsId":"H898"},{"label":"em>and</em> holdest thy tongue","strongsId":"H2790"},{"label":"when the wicked","strongsId":"H7563"},{"label":"devoureth","strongsId":"H1104"}]},{"id":"Hab|1|14","reference":"Habakkuk 1:14","number":14,"text":"And makest men as the fishes of the sea, as the creeping things, <em>that have</em> no ruler","strongs":[{"label":"And makest","strongsId":"H6213"},{"label":"men","strongsId":"H120"},{"label":"as the fishes","strongsId":"H1709"},{"label":"of the sea","strongsId":"H3220"},{"label":"as the creeping things","strongsId":"H7431"}]},{"id":"Hab|1|15","reference":"Habakkuk 1:15","number":15,"text":"They take up all of them with the angle, they catch them in their net, and gather them in their drag: therefore they rejoice and are glad.","strongs":[{"label":"They take up","strongsId":"H5927"},{"label":"all of them with the angle","strongsId":"H2443"},{"label":"they catch","strongsId":"H1641"},{"label":"them in their net","strongsId":"H2764"},{"label":"and gather","strongsId":"H622"},{"label":"them in their drag","strongsId":"H4365"},{"label":"therefore they rejoice","strongsId":"H8055"}]},{"id":"Hab|1|16","reference":"Habakkuk 1:16","number":16,"text":"Therefore they sacrifice unto their net, and burn incense unto their drag; because by them their portion <em>is</em> fat, and their meat plenteous.","strongs":[{"label":"Therefore they sacrifice","strongsId":"H2076"},{"label":"unto their net","strongsId":"H2764"},{"label":"and burn incense","strongsId":"H6999"},{"label":"unto their drag","strongsId":"H4365"},{"label":"because by them","strongsId":"H1992"},{"label":"their portion","strongsId":"H2506"},{"label":"em>is</em> fat","strongsId":"H8082"},{"label":"and their meat","strongsId":"H3978"}]},{"id":"Hab|1|17","reference":"Habakkuk 1:17","number":17,"text":"Shall they therefore empty their net, and not spare continually to slay the nations?","strongs":[{"label":"Shall they therefore empty","strongsId":"H7324"},{"label":"their net","strongsId":"H2764"},{"label":"and not spare","strongsId":"H2550"},{"label":"continually","strongsId":"H8548"},{"label":"to slay","strongsId":"H2026"}]}]},{"number":2,"verses":[{"id":"Hab|2|1","reference":"Habakkuk 2:1","number":1,"text":"I will stand upon my watch, and set me upon the tower, and will watch to see what he will say unto me, and what I shall answer when I am reproved.","strongs":[{"label":"I will stand","strongsId":"H5975"},{"label":"upon my watch","strongsId":"H4931"},{"label":"and set","strongsId":"H3320"},{"label":"me upon the tower","strongsId":"H4692"},{"label":"and will watch","strongsId":"H6822"},{"label":"to see","strongsId":"H7200"},{"label":"what he will say","strongsId":"H1696"},{"label":"unto me, and what I shall answer","strongsId":"H7725"}]},{"id":"Hab|2|2","reference":"Habakkuk 2:2","number":2,"text":"And the LORD answered me, and said, Write the vision, and make <em>it</em> plain upon tables, that he may run that readeth","strongs":[{"label":"And the LORD","strongsId":"H3068"},{"label":"answered","strongsId":"H6030"},{"label":"me, and said","strongsId":"H559"},{"label":"Write","strongsId":"H3789"},{"label":"the vision","strongsId":"H2377"},{"label":"and make <em>it</em> plain","strongsId":"H874"},{"label":"upon tables","strongsId":"H3871"},{"label":"that he may run","strongsId":"H7323"}]},{"id":"Hab|2|3","reference":"Habakkuk 2:3","number":3,"text":"For the vision <em>is</em> yet for an appointed time, but at the end it shall speak, and not lie: though it tarry, wait for it; because it will surely come, it will not tarry.","strongs":[{"label":"For the vision","strongsId":"H2377"},{"label":"em>is</em> yet for an appointed time","strongsId":"H4150"},{"label":"but at the end","strongsId":"H7093"},{"label":"it shall speak","strongsId":"H6315"},{"label":"and not lie","strongsId":"H3576"},{"label":"though it tarry","strongsId":"H4102"},{"label":"wait","strongsId":"H2442"},{"label":"for it; because it will surely","strongsId":"H935"},{"label":"come","strongsId":"H935"}]},{"id":"Hab|2|4","reference":"Habakkuk 2:4","number":4,"text":"Behold, his soul <em>which</em> is lifted up is not upright in him: but the just shall live by his faith.","strongs":[{"label":"Behold, his soul","strongsId":"H5315"},{"label":"em>which</em> is lifted up","strongsId":"H6075"},{"label":"is not upright","strongsId":"H3474"},{"label":"in him: but the just","strongsId":"H6662"},{"label":"shall live","strongsId":"H2421"}]},{"id":"Hab|2|5","reference":"Habakkuk 2:5","number":5,"text":"Yea also, because he transgresseth by wine, <em>he is</em> a proud man, neither keepeth at home, who enlargeth his desire as hell, and <em>is</em> as death, and cannot be satisfied, but gathereth unto him all nations, and heapeth unto him all people:","strongs":[{"label":"Yea also, because he transgresseth","strongsId":"H898"},{"label":"by wine","strongsId":"H3196"},{"label":"em>he is</em> a proud","strongsId":"H3093"},{"label":"man","strongsId":"H1397"},{"label":"neither keepeth at home","strongsId":"H5115"},{"label":"who enlargeth","strongsId":"H7337"},{"label":"his desire","strongsId":"H5315"},{"label":"as hell","strongsId":"H7585"},{"label":"and <em>is</em> as death","strongsId":"H4194"},{"label":"and cannot be satisfied","strongsId":"H7646"},{"label":"but gathereth","strongsId":"H622"},{"label":"unto him all nations","strongsId":"H1471"},{"label":"and heapeth","strongsId":"H6908"}]},{"id":"Hab|2|6","reference":"Habakkuk 2:6","number":6,"text":"Shall not all these take up a parable against him, and a taunting proverb against him, and say, Woe to him that increaseth <em>that which is</em> not his! how long? and to him that ladeth himself with thick clay!","strongs":[{"label":"Shall not all these take up","strongsId":"H5375"},{"label":"a parable","strongsId":"H4912"},{"label":"against him, and a taunting","strongsId":"H4426"},{"label":"proverb","strongsId":"H2420"},{"label":"against him, and say","strongsId":"H559"},{"label":"Woe","strongsId":"H1945"},{"label":"to him that increaseth","strongsId":"H7235"},{"label":"em>that which is</em> not his! how long? and to him that ladeth","strongsId":"H3513"}]},{"id":"Hab|2|7","reference":"Habakkuk 2:7","number":7,"text":"Shall they not rise up suddenly that shall bite thee, and awake that shall vex thee, and thou shalt be for booties","strongs":[{"label":"Shall they not rise up","strongsId":"H6965"},{"label":"suddenly","strongsId":"H6621"},{"label":"that shall bite","strongsId":"H5391"},{"label":"thee, and awake","strongsId":"H3364"},{"label":"that shall vex","strongsId":"H2111"}]},{"id":"Hab|2|8","reference":"Habakkuk 2:8","number":8,"text":"Because thou hast spoiled many nations, all the remnant of the people shall spoil thee; because of men's blood, and <em>for</em> the violence of the land, of the city, and of all that dwell","strongs":[{"label":"Because thou hast spoiled","strongsId":"H7997"},{"label":"many","strongsId":"H7227"},{"label":"nations","strongsId":"H1471"},{"label":"all the remnant","strongsId":"H3499"},{"label":"of the people","strongsId":"H5971"},{"label":"shall spoil","strongsId":"H7997"},{"label":"thee; because of men's","strongsId":"H120"},{"label":"blood","strongsId":"H1818"},{"label":"and <em>for</em> the violence","strongsId":"H2555"},{"label":"of the land","strongsId":"H776"},{"label":"of the city","strongsId":"H7151"}]},{"id":"Hab|2|9","reference":"Habakkuk 2:9","number":9,"text":"Woe to him that coveteth an evil covetousness to his house, that he may set his nest on high, that he may be delivered from the power of evil!","strongs":[{"label":"Woe","strongsId":"H1945"},{"label":"to him that coveteth","strongsId":"H1214"},{"label":"an evil","strongsId":"H7451"},{"label":"covetousness","strongsId":"H1215"},{"label":"to his house","strongsId":"H1004"},{"label":"that he may set","strongsId":"H7760"},{"label":"his nest","strongsId":"H7064"},{"label":"on high","strongsId":"H4791"},{"label":"that he may be delivered","strongsId":"H5337"},{"label":"from the power","strongsId":"H3709"}]},{"id":"Hab|2|10","reference":"Habakkuk 2:10","number":10,"text":"Thou hast consulted shame to thy house by cutting off many people, and hast sinned <em>against</em> thy soul.","strongs":[{"label":"Thou hast consulted","strongsId":"H3289"},{"label":"shame","strongsId":"H1322"},{"label":"to thy house","strongsId":"H1004"},{"label":"by cutting off","strongsId":"H7096"},{"label":"many","strongsId":"H7227"},{"label":"people","strongsId":"H5971"},{"label":"and hast sinned","strongsId":"H2398"}]},{"id":"Hab|2|11","reference":"Habakkuk 2:11","number":11,"text":"For the stone shall cry out of the wall, and the beam out of the timber shall answer","strongs":[{"label":"For the stone","strongsId":"H68"},{"label":"shall cry out","strongsId":"H2199"},{"label":"of the wall","strongsId":"H7023"},{"label":"and the beam out","strongsId":"H3714"},{"label":"of the timber","strongsId":"H6086"}]},{"id":"Hab|2|12","reference":"Habakkuk 2:12","number":12,"text":"Woe to him that buildeth a town with blood, and stablisheth a city by iniquity!","strongs":[{"label":"Woe","strongsId":"H1945"},{"label":"to him that buildeth","strongsId":"H1129"},{"label":"a town","strongsId":"H5892"},{"label":"with blood","strongsId":"H1818"},{"label":"and stablisheth","strongsId":"H3559"},{"label":"a city","strongsId":"H7151"}]},{"id":"Hab|2|13","reference":"Habakkuk 2:13","number":13,"text":"Behold, <em>is it</em> not of the LORD of hosts that the people shall labour in the very fire, and the people shall weary themselves for very vanity?","strongs":[{"label":"Behold, <em>is it</em> not of the LORD","strongsId":"H3068"},{"label":"of hosts","strongsId":"H6635"},{"label":"that the people","strongsId":"H5971"},{"label":"shall labour","strongsId":"H3021"},{"label":"in the very","strongsId":"H1767"},{"label":"fire","strongsId":"H784"},{"label":"and the people","strongsId":"H3816"},{"label":"shall weary","strongsId":"H3286"},{"label":"themselves for very","strongsId":"H1767"}]},{"id":"Hab|2|14","reference":"Habakkuk 2:14","number":14,"text":"For the earth shall be filled with the knowledge of the glory of the LORD, as the waters cover the sea.","strongs":[{"label":"For the earth","strongsId":"H776"},{"label":"shall be filled","strongsId":"H4390"},{"label":"with the knowledge","strongsId":"H3045"},{"label":"of the glory","strongsId":"H3519"},{"label":"of the LORD","strongsId":"H3068"},{"label":"as the waters","strongsId":"H4325"},{"label":"cover","strongsId":"H3680"}]},{"id":"Hab|2|15","reference":"Habakkuk 2:15","number":15,"text":"Woe unto him that giveth his neighbour drink, that puttest thy bottle to <em>him</em>, and makest <em>him</em> drunken also, that thou mayest look on their nakedness!","strongs":[{"label":"Woe","strongsId":"H1945"},{"label":"unto him that giveth his neighbour","strongsId":"H7453"},{"label":"drink","strongsId":"H8248"},{"label":"that puttest","strongsId":"H5596"},{"label":"thy bottle","strongsId":"H2573"},{"label":"to <em>him</em>, and makest <em>him</em> drunken","strongsId":"H7937"},{"label":"also, that thou mayest look","strongsId":"H5027"}]},{"id":"Hab|2|16","reference":"Habakkuk 2:16","number":16,"text":"Thou art filled with shame for glory: drink thou also, and let thy foreskin be uncovered: the cup of the LORD'S right hand shall be turned unto thee, and shameful spewing <em>shall be</em> on thy glory.","strongs":[{"label":"Thou art filled","strongsId":"H7646"},{"label":"with shame","strongsId":"H7036"},{"label":"for glory","strongsId":"H3519"},{"label":"drink","strongsId":"H8354"},{"label":"thou also, and let thy foreskin be uncovered","strongsId":"H6188"},{"label":"the cup","strongsId":"H3563"},{"label":"of the LORD'S","strongsId":"H3068"},{"label":"right hand","strongsId":"H3225"},{"label":"shall be turned","strongsId":"H5437"},{"label":"unto thee, and shameful spewing","strongsId":"H7022"}]},{"id":"Hab|2|17","reference":"Habakkuk 2:17","number":17,"text":"For the violence of Lebanon shall cover thee, and the spoil of beasts, <em>which</em> made them afraid, because of men's blood, and for the violence of the land, of the city, and of all that dwell","strongs":[{"label":"For the violence","strongsId":"H2555"},{"label":"of Lebanon","strongsId":"H3844"},{"label":"shall cover","strongsId":"H3680"},{"label":"thee, and the spoil","strongsId":"H7701"},{"label":"of beasts","strongsId":"H929"},{"label":"em>which</em> made them afraid","strongsId":"H2865"},{"label":"because of men's","strongsId":"H120"},{"label":"blood","strongsId":"H1818"},{"label":"and for the violence","strongsId":"H2555"},{"label":"of the land","strongsId":"H776"},{"label":"of the city","strongsId":"H7151"}]},{"id":"Hab|2|18","reference":"Habakkuk 2:18","number":18,"text":"What profiteth the graven image that the maker thereof hath graven it; the molten image, and a teacher of lies, that the maker of his work trusteth therein, to make dumb idols?","strongs":[{"label":"What profiteth","strongsId":"H3276"},{"label":"the graven image","strongsId":"H6459"},{"label":"that the maker","strongsId":"H3335"},{"label":"thereof hath graven","strongsId":"H6458"},{"label":"it; the molten image","strongsId":"H4541"},{"label":"and a teacher","strongsId":"H3384"},{"label":"of lies","strongsId":"H8267"},{"label":"that the maker","strongsId":"H3335"},{"label":"of his work","strongsId":"H3336"},{"label":"trusteth","strongsId":"H982"},{"label":"therein, to make","strongsId":"H6213"},{"label":"dumb","strongsId":"H483"}]},{"id":"Hab|2|19","reference":"Habakkuk 2:19","number":19,"text":"Woe unto him that saith to the wood, Awake; to the dumb stone, Arise, it shall teach! Behold, it <em>is</em> laid over with gold and silver, and <em>there is</em> no breath at all in the midst","strongs":[{"label":"Woe","strongsId":"H1945"},{"label":"unto him that saith","strongsId":"H559"},{"label":"to the wood","strongsId":"H6086"},{"label":"Awake","strongsId":"H6974"},{"label":"to the dumb","strongsId":"H1748"},{"label":"stone","strongsId":"H68"},{"label":"Arise","strongsId":"H5782"},{"label":"it shall teach","strongsId":"H3384"},{"label":"Behold, it <em>is</em> laid","strongsId":"H8610"},{"label":"over with gold","strongsId":"H2091"},{"label":"and silver","strongsId":"H3701"},{"label":"and <em>there is</em> no breath","strongsId":"H7307"}]},{"id":"Hab|2|20","reference":"Habakkuk 2:20","number":20,"text":"But the LORD <em>is</em> in his holy temple: let all the earth keep silence before","strongs":[{"label":"But the LORD","strongsId":"H3068"},{"label":"em>is</em> in his holy","strongsId":"H6944"},{"label":"temple","strongsId":"H1964"},{"label":"let all the earth","strongsId":"H776"},{"label":"keep silence","strongsId":"H2013"}]}]},{"number":3,"verses":[{"id":"Hab|3|1","reference":"Habakkuk 3:1","number":1,"text":"A prayer of Habakkuk the prophet upon Shigionoth.","strongs":[{"label":"A prayer","strongsId":"H8605"},{"label":"of Habakkuk","strongsId":"H2265"},{"label":"the prophet","strongsId":"H5030"}]},{"id":"Hab|3|2","reference":"Habakkuk 3:2","number":2,"text":"O LORD, I have heard thy speech, <em>and</em> was afraid: O LORD, revive thy work in the midst of the years, in the midst of the years make known; in wrath remember mercy.","strongs":[{"label":"O LORD","strongsId":"H3068"},{"label":"I have heard","strongsId":"H8085"},{"label":"thy speech","strongsId":"H8088"},{"label":"em>and</em> was afraid","strongsId":"H3372"},{"label":"O LORD","strongsId":"H3068"},{"label":"revive","strongsId":"H2421"},{"label":"thy work","strongsId":"H6467"},{"label":"in the midst","strongsId":"H7130"},{"label":"of the years","strongsId":"H8141"},{"label":"in the midst","strongsId":"H7130"},{"label":"of the years","strongsId":"H8141"},{"label":"make known","strongsId":"H3045"},{"label":"in wrath","strongsId":"H7267"},{"label":"remember","strongsId":"H2142"}]},{"id":"Hab|3|3","reference":"Habakkuk 3:3","number":3,"text":"God came from Teman, and the Holy One from mount Paran. Selah. His glory covered the heavens, and the earth was full of his praise.","strongs":[{"label":"God","strongsId":"H433"},{"label":"came","strongsId":"H935"},{"label":"from Teman","strongsId":"H8487"},{"label":"and the Holy One","strongsId":"H6918"},{"label":"from mount","strongsId":"H2022"},{"label":"Paran","strongsId":"H6290"},{"label":"Selah","strongsId":"H5542"},{"label":"His glory","strongsId":"H1935"},{"label":"covered","strongsId":"H3680"},{"label":"the heavens","strongsId":"H8064"},{"label":"and the earth","strongsId":"H776"},{"label":"was full","strongsId":"H4390"}]},{"id":"Hab|3|4","reference":"Habakkuk 3:4","number":4,"text":"And <em>his</em> brightness was as the light; he had horns <em>coming</em> out of his hand: and there <em>was</em> the hiding of his power.","strongs":[{"label":"And <em>his</em> brightness","strongsId":"H5051"},{"label":"was as the light","strongsId":"H216"},{"label":"he had horns","strongsId":"H7161"},{"label":"em>coming</em> out of his hand","strongsId":"H3027"},{"label":"and there <em>was</em> the hiding","strongsId":"H2253"}]},{"id":"Hab|3|5","reference":"Habakkuk 3:5","number":5,"text":"Before him went the pestilence, and burning coals went forth at his feet.","strongs":[{"label":"Before","strongsId":"H6440"},{"label":"him went","strongsId":"H3212"},{"label":"the pestilence","strongsId":"H1698"},{"label":"and burning coals","strongsId":"H7565"},{"label":"went forth","strongsId":"H3318"}]},{"id":"Hab|3|6","reference":"Habakkuk 3:6","number":6,"text":"He stood, and measured the earth: he beheld, and drove asunder the nations; and the everlasting mountains were scattered, the perpetual hills did bow: his ways <em>are</em> everlasting.","strongs":[{"label":"He stood","strongsId":"H5975"},{"label":"and measured","strongsId":"H4128"},{"label":"the earth","strongsId":"H776"},{"label":"he beheld","strongsId":"H7200"},{"label":"and drove asunder","strongsId":"H5425"},{"label":"the nations","strongsId":"H1471"},{"label":"and the everlasting","strongsId":"H5703"},{"label":"mountains","strongsId":"H2042"},{"label":"were scattered","strongsId":"H6327"},{"label":"the perpetual","strongsId":"H5769"},{"label":"hills","strongsId":"H1389"},{"label":"did bow","strongsId":"H7817"},{"label":"his ways","strongsId":"H1979"}]},{"id":"Hab|3|7","reference":"Habakkuk 3:7","number":7,"text":"I saw the tents of Cushan in affliction: <em>and</em> the curtains of the land of Midian did tremble.","strongs":[{"label":"I saw","strongsId":"H7200"},{"label":"the tents","strongsId":"H168"},{"label":"of Cushan","strongsId":"H3572"},{"label":"in affliction","strongsId":"H205"},{"label":"em>and</em> the curtains","strongsId":"H3407"},{"label":"of the land","strongsId":"H776"},{"label":"of Midian","strongsId":"H4080"}]},{"id":"Hab|3|8","reference":"Habakkuk 3:8","number":8,"text":"Was the LORD displeased against the rivers? <em>was</em> thine anger against the rivers? <em>was</em> thy wrath against the sea, that thou didst ride upon thine horses <em>and</em> thy chariots of salvation?","strongs":[{"label":"Was the LORD","strongsId":"H3068"},{"label":"displeased","strongsId":"H2734"},{"label":"against the rivers","strongsId":"H5104"},{"label":"em>was</em> thine anger","strongsId":"H639"},{"label":"against the rivers","strongsId":"H5104"},{"label":"em>was</em> thy wrath","strongsId":"H5678"},{"label":"against the sea","strongsId":"H3220"},{"label":"that thou didst ride","strongsId":"H7392"},{"label":"upon thine horses","strongsId":"H5483"},{"label":"em>and</em> thy chariots","strongsId":"H4818"}]},{"id":"Hab|3|9","reference":"Habakkuk 3:9","number":9,"text":"Thy bow was made quite naked, <em>according</em> to the oaths of the tribes, <em>even thy</em> word. Selah. Thou didst cleave the earth with rivers.","strongs":[{"label":"Thy bow","strongsId":"H7198"},{"label":"was made quite","strongsId":"H6181"},{"label":"naked","strongsId":"H5783"},{"label":"em>according</em> to the oaths","strongsId":"H7621"},{"label":"of the tribes","strongsId":"H4294"},{"label":"em>even thy</em> word","strongsId":"H562"},{"label":"Selah","strongsId":"H5542"},{"label":"Thou didst cleave","strongsId":"H1234"},{"label":"the earth","strongsId":"H776"}]},{"id":"Hab|3|10","reference":"Habakkuk 3:10","number":10,"text":"The mountains saw thee, <em>and</em> they trembled: the overflowing of the water passed by: the deep uttered his voice, <em>and</em> lifted up his hands on high.","strongs":[{"label":"The mountains","strongsId":"H2022"},{"label":"saw","strongsId":"H7200"},{"label":"thee, <em>and</em> they trembled","strongsId":"H2342"},{"label":"the overflowing","strongsId":"H2230"},{"label":"of the water","strongsId":"H4325"},{"label":"passed by","strongsId":"H5674"},{"label":"the deep","strongsId":"H8415"},{"label":"uttered","strongsId":"H5414"},{"label":"his voice","strongsId":"H6963"},{"label":"em>and</em> lifted up","strongsId":"H5375"},{"label":"his hands","strongsId":"H3027"}]},{"id":"Hab|3|11","reference":"Habakkuk 3:11","number":11,"text":"The sun <em>and</em> moon stood still in their habitation: at the light of thine arrows they went, <em>and</em> at the shining of thy glittering spear.","strongs":[{"label":"The sun","strongsId":"H8121"},{"label":"em>and</em> moon","strongsId":"H3394"},{"label":"stood still","strongsId":"H5975"},{"label":"in their habitation","strongsId":"H2073"},{"label":"at the light","strongsId":"H216"},{"label":"of thine arrows","strongsId":"H2671"},{"label":"they went","strongsId":"H1980"},{"label":"em>and</em> at the shining","strongsId":"H5051"},{"label":"of thy glittering","strongsId":"H1300"}]},{"id":"Hab|3|12","reference":"Habakkuk 3:12","number":12,"text":"Thou didst march through the land in indignation, thou didst thresh the heathen in anger.","strongs":[{"label":"Thou didst march through","strongsId":"H6805"},{"label":"the land","strongsId":"H776"},{"label":"in indignation","strongsId":"H2195"},{"label":"thou didst thresh","strongsId":"H1758"},{"label":"the heathen","strongsId":"H1471"}]},{"id":"Hab|3|13","reference":"Habakkuk 3:13","number":13,"text":"Thou wentest forth for the salvation of thy people, <em>even</em> for salvation with thine anointed; thou woundedst the head out of the house of the wicked, by discovering the foundation unto the neck. Selah.","strongs":[{"label":"Thou wentest forth","strongsId":"H3318"},{"label":"for the salvation","strongsId":"H3468"},{"label":"of thy people","strongsId":"H5971"},{"label":"em>even</em> for salvation","strongsId":"H3468"},{"label":"with thine anointed","strongsId":"H4899"},{"label":"thou woundedst","strongsId":"H4272"},{"label":"the head","strongsId":"H7218"},{"label":"out of the house","strongsId":"H1004"},{"label":"of the wicked","strongsId":"H7563"},{"label":"by discovering","strongsId":"H6168"},{"label":"the foundation","strongsId":"H3247"},{"label":"unto the neck","strongsId":"H6677"}]},{"id":"Hab|3|14","reference":"Habakkuk 3:14","number":14,"text":"Thou didst strike through with his staves the head of his villages: they came out as a whirlwind to scatter me: their rejoicing <em>was</em> as to devour the poor secretly.","strongs":[{"label":"Thou didst strike through","strongsId":"H5344"},{"label":"with his staves","strongsId":"H4294"},{"label":"the head","strongsId":"H7218"},{"label":"of his villages","strongsId":"H6518"},{"label":"they came out as a whirlwind","strongsId":"H5590"},{"label":"to scatter","strongsId":"H6327"},{"label":"me: their rejoicing","strongsId":"H5951"},{"label":"em>was</em> as to devour","strongsId":"H398"},{"label":"the poor","strongsId":"H6041"}]},{"id":"Hab|3|15","reference":"Habakkuk 3:15","number":15,"text":"Thou didst walk through the sea with thine horses, <em>through</em> the heap of great waters.","strongs":[{"label":"Thou didst walk","strongsId":"H1869"},{"label":"through the sea","strongsId":"H3220"},{"label":"with thine horses","strongsId":"H5483"},{"label":"em>through</em> the heap","strongsId":"H2563"},{"label":"of great","strongsId":"H7227"}]},{"id":"Hab|3|16","reference":"Habakkuk 3:16","number":16,"text":"When I heard, my belly trembled; my lips quivered at the voice: rottenness entered into my bones, and I trembled in myself, that I might rest in the day of trouble: when he cometh up unto the people, he will invade them with his troops.","strongs":[{"label":"When I heard","strongsId":"H8085"},{"label":"my belly","strongsId":"H990"},{"label":"trembled","strongsId":"H7264"},{"label":"my lips","strongsId":"H8193"},{"label":"quivered","strongsId":"H6750"},{"label":"at the voice","strongsId":"H6963"},{"label":"rottenness","strongsId":"H7538"},{"label":"entered","strongsId":"H935"},{"label":"into my bones","strongsId":"H6106"},{"label":"and I trembled","strongsId":"H7264"},{"label":"in myself, that I might rest","strongsId":"H5117"},{"label":"in the day","strongsId":"H3117"},{"label":"of trouble","strongsId":"H6869"},{"label":"when he cometh up","strongsId":"H5927"},{"label":"unto the people","strongsId":"H5971"}]},{"id":"Hab|3|17","reference":"Habakkuk 3:17","number":17,"text":"Although the fig tree shall not blossom, neither <em>shall</em> fruit <em>be</em> in the vines; the labour of the olive shall fail, and the fields shall yield no meat; the flock shall be cut off from the fold, and <em>there shall be</em> no herd in the stalls:","strongs":[{"label":"Although the fig tree","strongsId":"H8384"},{"label":"shall not blossom","strongsId":"H6524"},{"label":"neither <em>shall</em> fruit","strongsId":"H2981"},{"label":"em>be</em> in the vines","strongsId":"H1612"},{"label":"the labour","strongsId":"H4639"},{"label":"of the olive","strongsId":"H2132"},{"label":"shall fail","strongsId":"H3584"},{"label":"and the fields","strongsId":"H7709"},{"label":"shall yield","strongsId":"H6213"},{"label":"no meat","strongsId":"H400"},{"label":"the flock","strongsId":"H6629"},{"label":"shall be cut off","strongsId":"H1504"},{"label":"from the fold","strongsId":"H4356"},{"label":"and <em>there shall be</em> no herd","strongsId":"H1241"}]},{"id":"Hab|3|18","reference":"Habakkuk 3:18","number":18,"text":"Yet I will rejoice in the LORD, I will joy in the God of my salvation.","strongs":[{"label":"Yet I will rejoice","strongsId":"H5937"},{"label":"in the LORD","strongsId":"H3068"},{"label":"I will joy","strongsId":"H1523"},{"label":"in the God","strongsId":"H430"}]},{"id":"Hab|3|19","reference":"Habakkuk 3:19","number":19,"text":"The LORD God <em>is</em> my strength, and he will make my feet like hinds' <em>feet</em>, and he will make me to walk upon mine high places. To the chief singer on my stringed instruments.","strongs":[{"label":"The LORD","strongsId":"H3069"},{"label":"God","strongsId":"H136"},{"label":"em>is</em> my strength","strongsId":"H2428"},{"label":"and he will make","strongsId":"H7760"},{"label":"my feet","strongsId":"H7272"},{"label":"like hinds'","strongsId":"H355"},{"label":"em>feet</em>, and he will make me to walk","strongsId":"H1869"},{"label":"upon mine high places","strongsId":"H1116"},{"label":"To the chief singer","strongsId":"H5329"}]}]}]}
